data.description: Offering a truly unique investment opportunity in Hartford's highly sought-after South End, 28 Eaton St is a multifamily that has been meticulously renovated and upgraded. Gross over $4150 per month through three units with separate utilities and potential for garage rental as well. Brand new roof and all units were fully renovated in 2022 with new kitchens, bathrooms, flooring, paint, and are in perfect condition. Each unit has laundry, closets, enclosed balcony, and parking. Basement is spotless and includes newer water heaters and a new 1st floor furnace and upgraded electrical panel. The 1st-floor tenant currently handles lawn mowing making this an excellent turn-key low maintenance investment property.
